{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/filemonitorsignalname\/changed"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"changed","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"watchMoves"},{"text":" on a directory monitor, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the information is available (and if supported by the backend),","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"eventType","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" may be "},{"code":"renamed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"movedIn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"movedOut"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In all cases ","type":"text"},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be a child of the monitored directory.  For"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"renames, ","type":"text"},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be the old name and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"otherFile"},{"type":"text","text":" is the new"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"name.  For “moved in” events, ","type":"text"},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the name of the file that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"appeared and ","type":"text"},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the old name that it was moved from (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"another directory).  For “moved out” events, ","type":"text"},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the name of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the file that used to be in this directory and ","type":"text"},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"name of the file at its new location."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It makes sense to treat ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"movedIn"},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"equivalent to "},{"code":"created","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"movedOut","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" as equivalent to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"deleted","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", with extra information."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"renamed"},{"text":" is equivalent to a delete\/create","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pair.  This is exactly how the events will be reported in the case"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"watchMoves"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is not in use."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If using the deprecated flag ","type":"text"},{"code":"sendMoved","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"eventType"},{"text":" is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"moved","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set to a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File","isActive":true},{"text":" containing the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"old path, and "},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set to a "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" containing the new path."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In all the other cases, ","type":"text"},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set to "},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Emitted when "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"text":" has been changed.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"case","externalID":"s:3GIO21FileMonitorSignalNameO7changedyA2CmF","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"changed"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Case","title":"FileMonitorSignalName.changed"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorSignalName"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorSignalName\/changed","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/InputStream":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InputStream","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GInputStream"},{"type":"text","text":" is a base class for implementing streaming input."}],"title":"InputStream","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/inputstream","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"InputStream","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"InputStream","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/FileMonitorSignalName/changed":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorSignalName\/changed","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/filemonitorsignalname\/changed","abstract":[{"text":"Emitted when ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"type":"text","text":" has been changed."}],"title":"FileMonitorSignalName.changed","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"changed"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/FileMonitorSignalName":{"role":"symbol","title":"FileMonitorSignalName","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/filemonitorsignalname","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FileMonitorSignalName"}],"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorSignalName","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"FileMonitorSignalName"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/File":{"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GFile"},{"type":"text","text":" is a high level abstraction for manipulating files on a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"virtual file system. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GFile"},{"type":"text","text":"s are lightweight, immutable objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that do no I\/O upon creation. It is necessary to understand that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GFile"},{"type":"text","text":" objects do not represent files, merely an identifier for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"file. All file content I\/O is implemented as streaming operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(see [class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InputStream","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"] and [class","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStream"},{"type":"text","text":"])."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/file","title":"File","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"File","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"File"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OutputStream":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OutputStream","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"code":"GOutputStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is a base class for implementing streaming output."}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/outputstream","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStream","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OutputStream","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OutputStream","kind":"identifier"}]}}}